Select one of these orders: noble, secular or templar. You gain one of the following Traits by order:
   As a noble Chevalier: whenever you fail a Martial Melee or Education Test, you can re-roll to generate a better result, but must accept the outcome;
   As a secular Chevalier: whenever you fail a Martial Melee or Ride Test, you can re-roll to generate a better result, but must accept the outcome;
   As a templar Chevalier: whenever you fail a Martial Melee or Resolve Test, you can re-roll to generate a better result, but must accept the outcome.
